code: import{isNumber,isString}from'lodash';class Prettify{price(value){if(!isNumber(value))return'0 $';const string=Math.round(value).toString();const separator=' ';return string.replace(/(\d{1,3}(?=(?:\d\d\d)+(?!\d)))/g,"$1".concat(separator)).concat(' $');}materials(value){if(!isNumber(value))return'0 mat.';const string=Math.round(value).toString();const separator=' ';return string.replace(/(\d{1,3}(?=(?:\d\d\d)+(?!\d)))/g,"$1".concat(separator)).concat(' mat.');}phoneNumber(value){if(!isString(value))return'';const str=value.replace(/[^0-9]/gim,'');const numberChunks=str.match(/.{1,3}/g);if(numberChunks)return numberChunks.join(' ');return'';}}export default new Prettify();
